# agents.locator
# Purpose: help tools (OpenClaw/Codex/OpenCode) quickly locate canonical governance files.
# This file contains NO secrets.

# Discovery policy: try in order; load all that exist; apply most-restrictive merge.

# 1) Repo-local (closest)
1) ./agents.md
2) ./.claude/agents.md
3) ./docs/agents.md
4) apps/**/agents.md

# 2) Workspace root (local dev), if present
5) ~/dev/agents.md
6) ~/dev/SYSTEMRULES.md
7) ~/dev/NETWORK.md
8) ~/dev/PORTS.md

# 3) User-level global (local OS / WSL)
9) ~/.config/devinecreations/agents/agents.md
10) ~/.agents/agents.md

# 4) Server multi-user shared (preferred server pattern)
11) /home/<current_user>/shared/agents/agents.md
12) /home/<current_user>/shared/agents/SYSTEMRULES.md
13) /home/<current_user>/shared/agents/NETWORK.md
14) /home/<current_user>/shared/agents/PORTS.md

# 5) Server shared canonical (optional)
15) /opt/devinecreations/agents/agents.md

# Optional companion identity layer (try alongside agents.md when present)
- agents.identity.md
- codex.guardrails.md

# Windows equivalents (informational)
- %USERPROFILE%\.devinecreations\agents\agents.md
- %APPDATA%\DevineCreations\agents\agents.md
